{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.720", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.120", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.200", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kommen wir zur\u00fcck zur Realit\u00e4t. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.160", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutschland ist die Wirtschaftskraft Europas: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.280", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Bruttoinlandsprodukt w\u00e4chst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.560", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Binnennachfrage ist unver\u00e4ndert hoch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.520", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Wirtschaft ist mehr als ausgelastet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.000", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Wirtschaftsleistung\u00a02018 soll noch einmal um 2,2\u00a0Prozent zulegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.480", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dem Haushaltsentwurf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.720", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den wir heute beraten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schaffen wir die Grundlage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.480", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieser Aufschwung auch anhalten kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.520", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir ziehen nicht mit der Gie\u00dfkanne durchs Land. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.840", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir folgen auch nicht den Rufen der Wirtschaft nach Steuerentlastungen in einer Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.320", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der sich Unternehmen vor Auftr\u00e4gen kaum retten k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.280", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht nicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.880", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Konzerne in einer Phase der Hochkonjunktur zu entlasten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.880", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vielmehr geht es darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.200", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Mittel zielgerichtet einzusetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Investitionskraft kleiner und mittlerer Unternehmen zu befl\u00fcgeln und die Zukunftsbranchen unseres Landes zu st\u00e4rken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.960", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen die Ausgaben f\u00fcr Forschung und Entwicklung bis 2025 auf 3,5\u00a0Prozent des Bruttoinlandsproduktes steigern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.200", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ambitioniert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.160", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die 26\u00a0Millionen Euro, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.080", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir daf\u00fcr zus\u00e4tzlich in den Haushalt eingestellt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind ein Einstieg. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.320", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Signal lautet also: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.720", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir l\u00f6sen die Investitionsbremse."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.680", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutschland muss zuk\u00fcnftig zu den f\u00fchrenden Innovationsstandorten geh\u00f6ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir d\u00fcrfen nicht zusehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.680", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie uns S\u00fcdkorea oder China den Rang ablaufen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.560", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Voraussetzung daf\u00fcr ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Mittel auch sinnvoll eingesetzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein guter Ansatz ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.480", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Anteil kleiner und mittlerer Betriebe an Forschung und Entwicklung deutlich zu steigern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.440", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss sich dann aber auch in F\u00f6rderprogrammen wie ZIM und IGF widerspiegeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.360", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beide beinhalten Kooperationsm\u00f6glichkeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.840", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und diese erzielen bekanntlich den gr\u00f6\u00dften Output. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.720", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ZIM gilt zudem als das Best-Practice-Beispiel und erfreut sich einer ungebrochenen Nachfrage. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.080", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch Herr Minister Altmaier hat heute in seiner Pressemitteilung ZIM sehr gelobt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.320", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch dann d\u00fcrfen wir nat\u00fcrlich nicht anfangen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.640", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an dieser Stelle zu sparen und die Mittel herunterzufahren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.400", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.040", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da ist Luft nach oben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.240", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Koalitionsvertrag\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.400", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das freut mich besonders\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.280", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind zum ersten Mal soziale Innovationen erw\u00e4hnt und finden dort ihren Platz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.560", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb w\u00e4re es folgerichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.720", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit F\u00f6rderprogrammen Anreize f\u00fcr soziale Innovationen zu schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.440", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leider wird das Thema meiner Meinung nach immer noch stiefm\u00fctterlich behandelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.560", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde mir w\u00fcnschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.040", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das BMWi die Chancen der sozialen Innovationen erkennt und hier st\u00e4rker f\u00f6rdert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.440", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch mit der steuerlichen Forschungsf\u00f6rderung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.480", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir vereinbart haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.800", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schaffen wir zus\u00e4tzliche Anreize. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.760", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben auch hier im Koalitionsvertrag zielgerichtet die kleinen und mittleren Betriebe einbezogen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.400", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.400", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Betriebe die Personalkosten im Bereich der Forschung absetzen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.840", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein gezielter und ganz neuer Ansatz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.520", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Investition des Staates, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.440", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit KMUs f\u00fcr die Zukunft gewappnet sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.640", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.720", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dar\u00fcber hinaus sendet der Haushaltsentwurf klare Signale an die Gr\u00fcnderszene. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.880", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir stocken gerade das EXIST-Programm auf und f\u00f6rdern junge Gr\u00fcnder aus dem Hochschulbereich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.400", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir erm\u00f6glichen mithilfe der KfW, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.480", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass f\u00fcr die Wachstumsphase innovativer Start-ups mehr Wagniskapital zur Verf\u00fcgung gestellt wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.480", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier ist eine L\u00fccke entstanden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.880", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die oft von ausl\u00e4ndischen Kapitalgebern gef\u00fcllt worden ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.760", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcnsche mir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.040", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass innovatives Know-how im Land bleibt und nicht von der Silicon Valley Bank gesichert wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.520", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die aktuell ihren Markteintritt in Deutschland vorbereitet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.680", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine unserer wichtigsten Aufgaben liegt unmittelbar vor uns\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.520", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Vorredner haben darauf hingewiesen\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.760", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Weiterentwicklung eines gesamtdeutschen F\u00f6rdersystems f\u00fcr strukturschwache Regionen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.400", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben in diesem Haus mehrfach betont, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.800", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass F\u00f6rdermittel nicht l\u00e4nger nach Himmelsrichtungen vergeben werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.800", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern gezielt in die strukturschwachen Gebiete flie\u00dfen sollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.080", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Zeit dr\u00e4ngt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.960", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ab 2020 muss das neue Programm im Einsatz sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.560", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit Blick auf den kommenden Haushalt geh\u00f6rt f\u00fcr mich eine solche Strukturf\u00f6rderung nat\u00fcrlich ins Wirtschaftsministerium."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.440", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "312.080", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Haushaltsentwurf hat die richtigen Ans\u00e4tze und bietet eine gute Grundlage f\u00fcr unsere weiteren Beratungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "312.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "313.400", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei allem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "313.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.080", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir noch tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "315.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "316.520", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bleibt eines klar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "316.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "318.440", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir setzen den Rahmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "318.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "323.720", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Innovation und Fortschritt aber m\u00fcssen letztendlich aus der Wirtschaft selber kommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "323.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.760", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
